    "content": "Wonderful\r\nEverclear\r\nAlbum: Songs From an American Movie.  Part 1\r\nTabbed by: wsu182@hotmail.com\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]Intro (follows piano)\r\nG-----------------\r\nD---5-------------\r\nA------5--3--5---\r\nE------------------[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse\r\nG-------------------------------\r\nD--------2--------2-----2----2-\r\nA------------5------3------5---\r\nE---3---------------------------[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus \"Promises mean everything...I hate everything\"\r\nG------------------------------------------\r\nD------------------------------------------2--\r\nA---33333333-55555555--------------\r\nE---------------------------------3333-----[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]\"Everything is wonderful now...Na na na na na\"\r\nG--------------------------------------------\r\nD--------222--------222--------222-------\r\nA--------------555---------333------555--\r\nE---333-------------------------------------[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]\"I just want my life to be the same...just like it used to be\"\r\nG-------------\r\nD---5--4--2-\r\nA------------\r\nE------------[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]\"No...No\"  & Outro\r\nG--------------\r\nD--------------\r\nA--------------\r\nE---333-000--[/tab]\r\n\r\nThat's all of it, but I didn't really take the time to get the exact number \r\nof times each note is played, it's pretty simple to do that.  Enjoy.",
    "is_backing_track_under_review": false,
    "is_tab_ml": false
